+## P0 execution flow
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:4: trailing whitespace.
+
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:5: trailing whitespace.
+```mermaid
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:6: trailing whitespace.
+flowchart TD
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:7: trailing whitespace.
+    M[Mission JSON] --> S[Seed Git commit]
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:8: trailing whitespace.
+    S --> C[Candidate worktrees]
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:9: trailing whitespace.
+    C --> T[Standard tests]
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md:10: trailing whitespace.
