docs/BUILD_TRUTH.md:5: trailing whitespace.
+- **System:** PROMETHEUS V-1.1.1
docs/BUILD_TRUTH.md:6: trailing whitespace.
+- **Category:** candidate-to-proof recursive software engineering runtime
docs/BUILD_TRUTH.md:7: trailing whitespace.
